TY  - JOUR
TI  - Turnpike Theorems for a Generalized Leontief Model
AU  - McKenzie, Lionel W.
AB  - [Theorems are proved on the convergence of efficient paths in certain closed linear models of production to the Neumann ray (of maximal proportional expansion). Radner's theorem is generalized, in the first theorem, to convergence to a facet of the production cone which contains the Neumann ray. Then the weak convergence is extended in the second theorem from convergence to the facet to convergence to the ray itself.]
