TY  - JOUR
TI  - A Stochastic Programming Model
AU  - Kataoka, Shinji
AB  - [In this paper we propose a stochastic programming model which considers the distribution of an objective function and probabilistic constraints. Applying it to a transportation type problem, we derive a nonlinear programming problem constrained by linear inequalities and show that it can be solved by iteration of linear programming.]
